S.FORM: José Mário Vaz nalecuhan ciniza i 12 bulad 10 demiad 1957 a mihcaan, José Mário Vaz, u misingkiway a kawaw niza. u tabakiay a tapang nu kanatal (congtung) nu Guinea bissau ayza sa ci José Mário Vaz, micakat a demiad sa i 2014 a mihca 6 bulad 23 demiad. malalitin tu ihekalay atu zumaay a natinengan List of current heads of state and government
